{"tid":2165914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川樂山驚現異味濃霧 官方證實化工廠氯氣泄漏 強調沒爆炸","createTime":"2020-08-20T06:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T09:13:53.000Z","uid":13663,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"eda3179333142ab0bcff9cfd2e2fc1107181b934","tid":2165914,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:11:50.000Z","msg":"據五通橋區官方微博午間最新消息稱，8月20日上午8時許，五通橋沿涌斯江出現的刺激性氣味。五通橋官方表示，經排查現有危化企業均未見異常。從8點到11時，樂山市環境監測中心站、五通橋生態環境局對五通橋中心城區開展應急監測，所監測的氟化氫、VOCs、氯化氫、氯氣、氨氣指標均未出現超標數據。<br />\n<br />\n五通橋官方先前表示，經排查現有危化企業均未見異常。但據陸媒《界面新聞》報導，中共樂山市委宣傳部證實，該市五通橋區發生一起化工廠泄露事故，目前已經得到控制，暫無人員傷亡的報告。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<span class=\"red\">是泄露，不是爆炸</span>&rdquo;，樂山市委宣傳部人士強調說，由於泄露氣體存在異味，所以才引發部分當地居民擔憂。目前，有關部門正在排查泄露原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soundofhope.org/post/413305?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F413305%3Flang%3Db5&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=df3560b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.soundofhope.org/post/413305?lang=b5</a><br />\n<br />\n樂山又雙贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72550212b5c411236b54ce3b2b64a13009055f83","tid":2165914,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"水災洗池<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e559e448f0b556f378bbb8aaa4bd14689ad9492a","tid":2165914,"uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:13:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fiteray/status/1296280900146094081?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffiteray%2Fstatus%2F1296280900146094081%3Fs%3D21&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=50a1a41c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffiteray%2Fstatus%2F1296280900146094081%3Fs%3D21&h=ff1a493a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fiteray/status/